00:56:15.008 --> 00:56:18.412 line:-2 align:center
Leading game studios have plans to bring
their titles to the Mac,


1108
00:56:18.445 --> 00:56:21.448 line:-2 align:center
like Grid Legends,
taking advantage of Apple silicon


1109
00:56:21.481 --> 00:56:23.784 line:-1 align:center
to help you reach maximum speeds.


1110
00:56:23,817 --> 00:56:27,554 line:-2
Or Resident Evil Village,
