1113
00:56:34.161 --> 00:56:35.963 line:-1 align:center
to explore rich, expansive worlds


1114
00:56:35,996 --> 00:56:37,731 line:-1
on both Mac and iPad.


1115
00:56:37,764 --> 00:56:41,502 line:-2
Metal 3 is incredible,
