00:57:58,612 --> 00:58:01,348 line:-1
that was never before possible.


1143
00:58:01,381 --> 00:58:03,550 line:-2
You can, for example,
show that a point of interest


1144
00:58:03,584 --> 00:58:07,054 line:-2
is between the crosswalk
